BUILDING EvilPoison
===================

Using GNU make to build
-----------------------

1) Edit settings.make to suit what you want.  Instructions are included by any
   user-editable option.

2) Optionally (on Ubuntu) Run 'make ubuntu-dependencies'
     Alternatively install the equivalent of the following packages on your distribution,
     Build Requirements:
       apt-get install -y libx11-dev libxext-dev libxinerama-dev
     Unit Testing Requirements:
       apt-get install -y check
     Documentation Generation Requirements:
       apt-get install -y doxygen

3) Run 'make'

4) Run 'make install'

That's it.  The README file has information on starting evilpoison.
